WEBVTT

00:05:59.182 --> 00:06:01.652
Maisha ni mazuri.

00:06:02.646 --> 00:06:04.208
Kuna wakati yanavurugika,

00:06:04.232 --> 00:06:06.166
na hayatabiriki siku zote.

00:06:07.034 --> 00:06:08.237
Lakini kila kitu kitakuwa sawa

00:06:08.261 --> 00:06:11.046
unapokuwa na mfumo ambao utakusaidia kuyashinda yote.

00:06:11.513 --> 00:06:13.934
Nina imani kama mzigo wako ukiwa mzito sana,

00:06:13.958 --> 00:06:15.664
utaomba msaada, pia.

00:06:15.688 --> 00:06:16.855
Asante.

00:06:16.879 --> 00:06:19.761
(Makofi)